Sweet tooth vs. Strength goals? Why not both?! 🎂💪 @Danae.fit’s go-to birthday cake mug cake is soft, sweet, and packs 20g of protein with OIKOS PRO.

Mix in a mug:
🥄 ¼ cup self-rising flour
🥄 ½ cup OIKOS PRO Vanilla (save the rest for frosting)
🥄 1 tbsp coconut sugar
🥄 ½ tsp baking powder
🥄 ¼ cup milk of choice
🥄 1 tsp cake batter extract
✨ sprinkles (because obviously)

Microwave for 60 sec + 10-sec bursts until fluffy. Scoop on the rest of your OIKOS PRO, toss on some sprinkles and BOOM - your protein packed cake is ready! 

20g protein. No added sugar. Dessert that works as hard as you do.
